 * ğŸ‘ user done will enter the USER Id then in the right side of the input
 * filedğŸ‘ there will be a submit button named verify, when that user will click
 * in theğŸ‘ verify then the user id will come to the controller and will be
 * checked forğŸ‘ its existence and if false then will redirect to the transfer
 * page with alertğŸ‘ otherwise the name of that entered user id will be printed
 * and then there ğŸ‘ will be two method fast and fast cash. and one input amount
